    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最终前哨是一款生存策略基地建造游戏。您将带领着世界末日的最后幸存者。分配角色、制作工具并谨慎管理资源。建造建筑物、提升幸存者等级并巩固城镇以抵御成群的僵尸。您能生存几天？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/8d3af9d6aca8deafa7377953ff867002.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从 10 多个工作岗位中为每位幸存者选择合适的岗位，然后看着他们开始工作！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/3fc81176e5d81a6be55748bf63f435f0.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/3fc81176e5d81a6be55748bf63f435f0.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/3fc81176e5d81a6be55748bf63f435f0.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/4ae30c2ee89757ccc05dbd6207d4b821.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造和升级 12 种以上的建筑类型，扩大您的庞大定居点。为新幸存者建造重要的资源储存、生产建筑和住房。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/d1c55812d5c5240df29bd6684f2b8ac6.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/d1c55812d5c5240df29bd6684f2b8ac6.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/d1c55812d5c5240df29bd6684f2b8ac6.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/ebe2adfdf93bb19736b32697e1d425b4.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装饰您的防御工事，让 5 种以上的僵尸远离您的城墙。从一把刀开始，逐渐用机枪、弩和狙击手击倒成群的僵尸。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/67c9dbfc3276b331217f38d1eafa29a6.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/67c9dbfc3276b331217f38d1eafa29a6.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/67c9dbfc3276b331217f38d1eafa29a6.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/1b6ca46225f776b53837f0327519793a.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着您的营地的扩大，喂饱饥饿的幸存者。开始在田地里种植小麦，以克服城墙外日益减少的鹿群数量。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/03bc58beb3defe3fcf50e3ca550b8a9e.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/03bc58beb3defe3fcf50e3ca550b8a9e.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/03bc58beb3defe3fcf50e3ca550b8a9e.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/60d80c4fe148b343042502ef20b5573e.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在模拟天气和季节中度过严酷的干旱、寒冷的冬天和无情的雷暴。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/e246b2f1129e5c7ca3f9808859629e24.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/e246b2f1129e5c7ca3f9808859629e24.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/e246b2f1129e5c7ca3f9808859629e24.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/4e7956b97a63e3b1eb08a53283e26af5.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级幸存者的技能，以更有效地收集、防御和修复。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/759ad903cf2f15afa446e7d512d6e2c4.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/759ad903cf2f15afa446e7d512d6e2c4.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/759ad903cf2f15afa446e7d512d6e2c4.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
